@startuml
actor Engineer
participant "Project Config Page" as Page
participant "WorkspaceRuntimeBridge" as Bridge
participant "Config Service" as Config
participant "Disk YAML" as Disk
participant "Runtime Data" as Runtime

Engineer -> Page : Open Project Config
Page -> Bridge : request config model
Bridge -> Config : load current YAML
Config -> Disk : read file
Disk --> Config : raw YAML
Config --> Bridge : editable config model
Bridge --> Page : section data

Page -> Bridge : request live hardware values
Bridge -> Runtime : read live values
Runtime --> Bridge : live values
Bridge --> Page : mismatch-only Actual indicators

Engineer -> Page : Save changes
Page -> Bridge : submit edited config
Bridge -> Config : validate + version check + save
Config -> Disk : write <project_name>_<version>.yaml
Disk --> Config : saved path
Config --> Bridge : save result
Bridge --> Page : success + active file path
@enduml
